{
  "stem": "24171.6",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he remained there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh he took till he was-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was he 30, 35, something, when Hitler-- the things?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, he was born in '11.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the war was '40, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was already in the years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was not married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was the only one not married.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wasn't married-- with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he was kind of like a little delicate person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he got tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he didn't-- really, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I did found out after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because there was, from our village, was the guy between them, a Jewish guy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As he was-- you know, they were in-- in the basements some years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was very sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he passed away there in the-- that basements.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it was in Russia, in the middle of the way when they were marching against Hitler.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other one was there for-- you saw the soldier?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, as my husband said, he could have lifted-- a big man, a strong one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He died a awful, horrible death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- he was frozen, but he was alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pieces were falling off him-- hands, the nose, the ears.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was walking till he-- he could with the Czech legion, And-- [CRYING] --till-- I don't know how long.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as they say, as he said in Yiddish that he was dying alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Pieces were falling off him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was funny the way I found it-- you know, if-- found that out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I came to Prague already-- you know, well-- I'm gonna have to go back after the-- to talk back to-- with the-- to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came to Prague already, after the liberation-- and then everybody is, you know, running around like mad.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you see this one?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
